{"tid":883843,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[招聘]網上營業主管","createTime":"2018-10-31T06:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T11:55:01.000Z","uid":152029,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8bbb047eb7545cb05bb7934ff7ae2ac7736445","tid":883843,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"原本有兩條team，因為想擴張網上部門所以再開多條team<br />\n職位係Supervior，負責管理人同生意，條team會有人<br />\n<br />\n公司係PCCW 網上銷售部門，工作地點係葵興KC100寫字樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日番7個鐘（3PM-10PM）有1個鐘放飯，唔洗輪班輪休（固定星期日休息），最好係唔洗日曬雨淋擺街（全程寫字樓有自己位無須外出），同事都係廿零歲大家可以有傾有講。 <br />\n<br />\n直屬員工，底薪＋佣平均每月有＄15000－35000（底薪＄10000），一年有14日大假，有醫療卡福利，需要有銷售經驗(可以不同行業)，有管理方面經驗更佳(無亦可)，需要中五學歷同夠18歲或以上<br />\n<br />\n如果有做開銷售而又想試下做管理方面可以whatsapp 我了解<br />\n有咩直接搵我都可以解答各位巴打 <br />\n或者有問題可以留言我會盡力回覆所有問題 <br />\n<br />\n（WTS/CALL: 53 77 47 97）"},{"pid":"fc0e18d32287e58b395e90e6e3159bb147b83d0b","tid":883843,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個月入50k<br />\n你開到盡35k...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880a172e9bbd5a4684a0b2d9fb6842701455503b","tid":883843,"uid":126326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"冇銷售/管理經驗請唔請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c3b12683707aa8b6b6086fb3087b3e67c40d64","tid":883843,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0e18d32287e58b395e90e6e3159bb147b83d0b","tid":883843,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個月入50k<br />\n你開到盡35k...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"我唔想講大話老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝巴打幫推"},{"pid":"6ae4d1056bb666a1d3111f4cabdb2e4995dedd67","tid":883843,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880a172e9bbd5a4684a0b2d9fb6842701